      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but the engine would benefit from a tune-up and the tires will likely need replacing within the next few thousand miles. It is a solid car for someone willing to put in a little work.",
