      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, an exemplar of automotive preservation that remains in superlative condition. This specimen has been curated with the utmost care, presenting in a state that is indistinguishable from its original delivery. The exterior retains a mirror-like luster, complemented by an interior that remains entirely free of wear or compromise. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its class, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine automobile. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
