    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it's in absolutely pristine condition inside and out. No scratches, no dents, and it drives like an absolute dream! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been babied and is ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8. This unit delivers a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline, managed by eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is absolute; the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been proactively serviced with comprehensive documentation. The chassis is taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock that ensures surgical precision through corners. The 6-speed manual transmission provides a tactile connection to the drivetrain, free of synchro wear. Finished in factory-original paint with no evidence of thermal cycling on the carbon fiber roof, the interior remains in a preserved state with supple Novillo leather and intact bolsters. This is a turnkey, investment-grade specimen for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Service records complete. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
